{"word":"Abijam","slug":"abijam","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Abijam</b> <a href=\"#/H38\">H38</a> <br/> Called also Abijah and Abia.<br/> King of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=31'>1Ki 14:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=1'>1Ki 15:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=12&verse=16'>2Ch 12:16</a><br/> History of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=8'>1Ki 15:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=22'>2Ch 11:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13'>2Ch 13</a><br/> Succeeded by Asa<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=8'>1Ki 15:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=14&verse=1'>2Ch 14:1</a>"}]}